{"tid":2365574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Snapchat宣布永久終止特朗普帳戶","createTime":"2021-01-14T01:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T01:12:43.000Z","uid":52237,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"275de4b2435550791b6fa82d0fd32fb5538f3734","tid":2365574,"uid":52237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:00:13.000Z","msg":"Snapchat宣布永久終止特朗普帳戶<br />\n<br />\n即時通訊軟件Snapchat決定，即時永久終止美國總統特朗普的帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n公司表示，基於公共安全的考慮，以及特朗普試圖散布錯誤信息，仇恨言論和煽動暴力行為，作出永久終止帳戶的決定。<br />\n<br />\nSnapchat在上星期國會發生衝擊亂後，宣布無限期暫停特朗普的帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570316-20210114.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570316-20210114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=de02f960\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570316-20210114.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=71aa34a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570316-20210114.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a240920915cd42eb4300049612300508fc99508d","tid":2365574,"uid":256837,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"仲有人用嘅咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92129ee7eb305e109a28910bf357cad3b8ac7da8","tid":2365574,"uid":52237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"印象中SnapChat唔係第一次搞侵"},{"pid":"0e4f92260b8b93991109c09337c4aabd57bd1299","tid":2365574,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來侵有snapchat"},{"pid":"de70f0408c79e5341b1a4b8767fa5ffc1d04f4fd","tid":2365574,"uid"